llevar el caso con ella,

65
00:04:22,429 --> 00:04:23,930
interrumpirla y decir: "Cálmate".

66
00:04:24,014 --> 00:04:26,600
"Calmar"?

67
00:04:26,683 --> 00:04:31,605
